      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Bench-scale hemolysis index comparison — 5 operating points",
      "description": "Relative hemolysis index (RH) computed from CFD predictions compared against experimental measurements at 5 flow-speed combinations. All RH values fell below the 1.0 acceptance threshold. Mean absolute error across operating points was 0.043 RH units, within the pre-specified tolerance of 0.10."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/cpb-hemolysis-mesh-independence-001",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Mesh independence study — centrifugal pump hemolysis model",
      "description": "Three mesh refinement levels (coarse: 2.1M cells, medium: 5.8M cells, fine: 14.3M cells) evaluated. Grid convergence index (GCI) for the hemolysis index quantity of interest was 1.8% between medium and fine meshes, satisfying the MRL 2 discretization error requirement. Medium mesh selected for production runs."
    }
