      "rationale": "Coordinate measuring machine (CMM) inspection of the test pump confirmed geometric deviations from nominal CAD within ±0.05 mm across all critical surfaces. This level of equivalence is accepted at MRL 2 without further formal analysis. The CMM report is archived in the design history file."
