    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors achieved their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped to Gradation 1 and not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 expectations for a Class II CPB device. Validation results demonstrate RH predictions within ±0.10 of experimental measurements across all five operating points. The assessment team concludes that the CFD model has sufficient credibility to support the regulatory submission decision for worst-case hemolysis identification.",
